<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.8">
<l>vēyiṉ malipurai tōḷipiṉ ṉaikku maṇāḷaṉai</l>
<l>yāya perumpuka ḻellaiyi lātaṉa pāṭippōyk</l>
<l>kāyaṅ kaḻittavaṉ ṟāḷiṇaik kīḻppukuṅ kātalaṉ</l>
<l>māya maṉicarai yeṉcolla vallēṉeṉ vāykoṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I whose love it is to sing the bridegroom of Piṉṉai, she with shoulders</l>
<l>much resembling bamboo, for [his] existing great fame that is without bounds,</l>
<l>to go, discard the body [and] enter under his pair of feet,</l>
<l>how can I speak with my mouth about deceitful humans?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
